Standard Investment Research Hedged Equity Overseas Fund Form D
The Cayman Islands-based Standard Investment Research Hedged Equity Overseas Fund Ltd had published Form D because of $507.99 million offering. The date of first sale was 2008-01-01. The raised $507.99 million. The offering is still open. The total offering amount was $507.99 million. This form was filed on 2015-12-30. Standard Investment Research Hedged Equity Overseas Fund Ltd’s clarification was: The total amount sold and the number of investors disclosed in this Form D reflect sales to only US Investors. Withdrawals and/or redemptions are not taken into consideration.. 
 Standard Investment Research Hedged Equity Overseas Fund is based in Cayman Islands. The firm’s business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by Ben Fooshee Director. The company was incorporated more than five years ago. The filler’s address is: Sir Capital Management, L.P., 620 Eighth Avenue, 22Nd Floor, New York, Ny, New York, 10018. Shawn M. Brennan is the related person in the form and it has address: 620 Eighth Avenue, 22Nd Floor, New York, Ny, New York, 10018. Link to Standard Investment Research Hedged Equity Overseas Fund Filing: 000101297515000867.
Analysis of Standard Investment Research Hedged Equity Overseas Fund Offering
On average, firms in the Pooled Investment Fund sector, sell 37.80 % pooled investment fund interests. Standard Investment Research Hedged Equity Overseas Fund sold 100.00 % of the offering. The average offering size is $24.76 million for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund industry sector. The minimum investment for Standard Investment Research Hedged Equity Overseas Fund ‘s offering was $5000000.

